# APK Distribution Directory
#
# Place the built APK here as:
#   mnn-learning-latest.apk
#
# The file at this path is served at:
#   https://rawliet-app.uk/apk/mnn-learning-latest.apk
#
# WORKFLOW — update APK:
#   1. Build new APK via PWABuilder (https://pwabuilder.com)
#      pointing at: https://rawliet-app.uk
#   2. Replace this file:
#      apk/mnn-learning-latest.apk
#   3. Bump version in package.json
#   4. Update RELEASE_NOTES in download.html
#   5. Commit & push → Vercel auto-deploys
#
# NOTE: GitHub file size limit = 100 MB.
#       PWABuilder TWA APKs are typically 3–8 MB.
#       If APK exceeds limit, use Git LFS or GitHub Releases.
